    "body" : "<ol>\n<li>Single line <strong>comment</strong> <kbd>Ctrl</kbd> + <kbd>/</kbd></li>\n<li>Single line <strong>uncomment</strong> <kbd>Ctrl</kbd> + <kbd>/</kbd></li>\n</ol>\n\n<hr>\n\n<ol start=\"3\">\n<li>Multiline <strong>comment</strong> <kbd>Ctrl</kbd> + <kbd>Shift</kbd> + <kbd>/</kbd></li>\n<li>Multiline <strong>uncomment</strong> <kbd>Ctrl</kbd> + <kbd>Shift</kbd> + <kbd>\\</kbd> (note the backslash)</li>\n</ol>\n"
