      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
      "body" : "HAHA, by desesperally trying to uncomment in XML with <code>CTRL+SHIFT+\\ </code> , I discovered a new one <code>CTRL+ALT-GR+8</code> that seems to duplicate (vertical split) current edited file in 2 editors. Then you can see head and bottom of same file at same time"
