    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>The Ctrl + / stopped working for me in Eclipse 2021, due to conflicts of the same command.  If you go into Eclipse Preferences Generic Keys and then filter by &quot;comment&quot; you can then click on each Toggle Comment to see if there are any conflicts.  Remove conflicts by clicking on the command and clicking Unbind Command, and this fixed it for me: <a href=\"https://i.sstatic.net/dlfsJ.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://i.sstatic.net/dlfsJ.png\" alt=\"enter image description here\" /></a></p>\n"
